ZH: 这辆车是我的。
EN: This vehicle is mine.

ZH: 这辆车开得很快。
EN: This vehicle is driving very fast.

ZH: 看那辆红色的车！
EN: Look at that red vehicle!

ZH: 请关闭车辆门。
EN: Please close the vehicle door.

ZH: 上车前请系好安全带。
EN: Please fasten your seatbelt before getting in the vehicle.

ZH: 请将车辆停在合适的位置。
EN: Please park the vehicle in an appropriate spot.

ZH: 警察正在检查行驶的车辆。
EN: The police are inspecting the vehicles on the road.

ZH: 这辆公交车到站了。
EN: This bus has arrived at the station.

ZH: 请注意行人，以免发生车辆事故。
EN: Please watch out for pedestrians to prevent vehicle accidents.

ZH: 这辆卡车运送货物。
EN: This truck is transporting goods.

ZH: 那辆出租车在等待乘客。
EN: That taxi is waiting for passengers.

ZH: 我需要租一辆自行车。
EN: I need to rent a bicycle.

ZH: 这辆摩托车的引擎声音很吵。
EN: The engine noise of this motorcycle is very loud.

ZH: 这辆火车可以带我们到达目的地。
EN: This train can take us to our destination.

ZH: 这辆电动车非常环保。
EN: This electric vehicle is very environmentally friendly.

ZH: 他已经拥有了一辆新的轿车。
EN: He already owns a new sedan.

ZH: 我的车辆出现故障，需要维修。
EN: My vehicle has a malfunction and needs repairs.

ZH: 这辆自动驾驶汽车是未来的发展方向。
EN: This autonomous driving car is the future development direction.

ZH: 我每天乘坐公共交通工具上班，而不是开车。
EN: I take public transportation to work every day instead of driving a vehicle.

ZH: 那艘船和这辆汽车都具有载人功能。
EN: Both that boat and this vehicle are capable of carrying people.
